title: Previewing Ranked Power 5 Matchups in Week 7
description:
Wendi Nix, Sam Acho, and "Stanford" Steve Coughlin preview the packed slate of Top 25 matchups in Week 7. The crew dives into these critical ranked matchups occurring in each Power 5 conference, previewing 10 Penn State at 5 Michigan, 8 Oklahoma State at 12 TCU, 7 USC at 20 Utah, 15 NC State at 18 Syracuse, and 3 Alabama at 6 Tennessee. Also, Pete Thamel joins the show with an injury update for several key QBs, including Bryce Young, Will Levis, and Devin Leary.
